Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.75,0:13:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要用全部的力量把它干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.65,0:13:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现吧  出现吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.24,0:13:50.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼方之碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.22,0:13:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要过来  我最讨厌你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.62,0:14:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣银啊  爆裂吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.60,0:14:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个伊莉丝居然…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.37,0:14:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深月
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.12,0:14:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续攻击！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.97,0:14:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人  各就各位
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.33,0:14:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣银啊  爆裂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.13,0:14:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆裂吧  爆裂吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.69,0:14:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是现在
