Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.79,0:14:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贯穿吧  闪光！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.30,0:14:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实击中了
