Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.06,0:16:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(223,323)\fs18}Kiskanu
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.06,0:16:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇斯加努亦或是尤克特拉希尔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.98,0:16:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(297,323)\fs18}Yggdrasil
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.98,0:16:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤克特拉希尔？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.98,0:16:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是苍绿之…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.44,0:17:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.14,0:17:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙怎么可能会向人搭话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.41,0:17:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}再次确认
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.07,0:17:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要求你再次考虑我们之间的交易
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.14,0:17:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会给予我什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.22,0:17:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我又需要支付什么样的代价？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.23,0:17:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会给予你力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.64,0:17:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所需求的是歼灭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.43,0:17:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代价是  汝之记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.37,0:17:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要过来！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.99,0:17:45.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再阻止我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.68,0:17:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论发生什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.97,0:17:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都会是你的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.45,0:17:55.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能借给我你的力量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.60,0:17:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不杀掉我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.56,0:18:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就全部交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.92,0:18:08.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我渴求力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.71,0:18:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的交易  我接受了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.74,0:18:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连接确认
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.45,0:18:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(379,323)\fs18}Yggdrasil
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.45,0:18:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续交易！  尤克特拉希尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.70,0:18:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新连接  允准！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.60,0:18:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所需求的是歼灭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.47,0:18:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除我之外的龙类
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.12,0:18:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要比那个时候更强大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.89,0:18:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我提供的是力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.14,0:18:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代价为  汝之记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.10,0:18:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连接  切断！
