Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.27,0:19:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马尔杜克主炮  锁天之塔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.43,0:19:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开火！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.86,0:19:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终焉之矢
