Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.97,0:19:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陨星
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.08,0:19:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胜利了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.36,0:19:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.73,0:20:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢复原状了呢  物部
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.77,0:20:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物部
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.97,0:20:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了  物部少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.29,0:20:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然相信你就是没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.11,0:20:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你会做到如此程度呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.41,0:20:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么今后也要有劳你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.91,0:20:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的法夫纳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.93,0:20:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就是门禁了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.22,0:20:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.44,0:20:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就回来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.18,0:20:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体状态你也看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.11,0:20:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  让你担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.98,0:20:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是个坏哥哥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.66,0:20:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.75,0:21:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.15,0:21:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物部  你已经没事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.12,0:21:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是昏迷了一会而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.52,0:21:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找我什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.78,0:21:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我想问你我上次没有问完的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.64,0:21:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.93,0:21:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能和物部交朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.08,0:21:28.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不已经是朋友了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.73,0:21:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧  我什么时候和物部成为朋友了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.50,0:21:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「什么时候」啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.23,0:21:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就把你当成朋友了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.03,0:21:43.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物部你总是会给我最想要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.86,0:21:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.45,0:21:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  让我答谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.10,0:21:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  物部
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.83,0:23:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶！  我们把利维坦打倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.58,0:23:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我也成为了物部的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.83,0:23:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.50,0:23:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要把我的第一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.14,0:23:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？新的朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.83,0:23:59.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶！是物部的妻子！？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.26,0:24:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶！还要一起洗澡？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.82,0:24:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回  枪皇无尽的法夫纳
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.57,0:24:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙人缇娅
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.49,0:24:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物部  只顾着缇娅太不够意思了

